@startuml packages
title Package Dependency Boundaries
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

component "org.hestiastore.console.web.*" as Console
component "org.hestiastore.management.restjson.*" as Management
component "org.hestiastore.monitoring.micrometer.*" as Micrometer
component "org.hestiastore.monitoring.prometheus.*" as Prometheus
component "org.hestiastore.monitoring.json.api.*" as JsonApi
component "org.hestiastore.index.*" as Core

Console --> Management : HTTP management calls
Management --> Core : uses public index APIs
Management --> JsonApi : shared REST/JSON DTOs
Micrometer --> Core : monitoring bridge
Prometheus --> Core : monitoring bridge

note right of Core
  Core must not import:
  - org.hestiastore.monitoring.*
  - org.hestiastore.management.*
  - org.hestiastore.console.*
end note

@enduml
